## Installation

\`\`\`bash
npm install package-name
\`\`\`

## Quick Start

\`\`\`javascript
import { mainFunction } from 'package-name';

const result = mainFunction('input', { option: true });
console.log(result);
\`\`\`

## API Reference

### \`mainFunction(input, options?)\`

| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|-------------|
| input | string | Yes | The input to process |
| options | object | No | Configuration options |

**Options:**

| Key | Type | Default | Description |
|-----|------|---------|-------------|
| option | boolean | false | Enable feature |
| limit | number | 100 | Max results |

**Returns:** \`Result\` object

### \`helperFunction(data)\`

Utility function for common operations.

## TypeScript

Full TypeScript support with exported types:
\`\`\`typescript
import { mainFunction, type Options, type Result } from 'package-name';

const options: Options = { option: true };
const result: Result = mainFunction('input', options);
\`\`\`

## Browser Support

| Browser | Version |
|---------|---------|
| Chrome | 80+ |
| Firefox | 78+ |
| Safari | 14+ |
| Edge | 80+ |

